trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapAddressBinding"></xref> class.

Gets or sets a value representing the URI for the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Port"></xref> to which the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapAddressBinding"></xref> applies.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置一个值，表示的 URI <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.Port"> </xref>到<xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.SoapAddressBinding"></xref>适用。
包含 URI 的字符串。

trans-unit.source: The default value is an empty string ("").
